Overview:
The BMI Calculator app is designed to help users assess their Body Mass Index (BMI) quickly and accurately. By inputting their height and weight, users can determine their BMI and gain insights into their overall health and fitness levels.

BMI Calculation: The app calculates the BMI based on the user’s input.
Health Status: The app instantly provides the user’s BMI and corresponding health status (e.g., underweight, normal weight, overweight, or obese).
User-Friendly Interface: The app offers an intuitive and easy-to-use interface for a seamless experience.

Conclusion
The BMI Calculator app serves as a valuable tool for individuals who want to monitor their body mass index and make informed decisions about their health. 
